#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.binomial"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a binomial distribution."
msgstr "从二项分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a binomial distribution with specified parameters,"
" n trials and p probability of success where n an integer >= 0 and p is "
"in the interval [0,1]. (n may be input as a float, but it is truncated to"
" an integer in use)"
msgstr ""
"样本从具有指定参数的二项分布中抽取，n 次试验，成功概率为 p，其中 n 是大于"
"等于 0 的整数，p 在区间 [0,1] 内。（n 可以输入为浮点数，但使用时会被截断"
"为整数）"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:8 of
msgid ""
"Parameter of the distribution, >= 0. Floats are also accepted, but they "
"will be truncated to integers."
msgstr "分布的参数，>= 0。也接受浮点数，但会被截断为整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:11 of
msgid "Parameter of the distribution, >= 0 and <=1."
msgstr "分布的参数，>= 0 且 <=1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:13 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``n`` and ``p`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``mt.broadcast(n, p).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 是 ``None``（默认），当 ``n`` 和 ``p`` 都是标量时返回单个"
"值。否则，抽取 ``mt.broadcast(n, p).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:18 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上的期望块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:20 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:22 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:25 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized binomial distribution, "
"where each sample is equal to the number of successes over the n trials."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 从参数化的二项分布中抽取的样本，其中每个样本等于 n 次试验中的"
"成功次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.binom`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:32 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:35 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:36 of
msgid "The probability density for the binomial distribution is"
msgstr "二项分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:38 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"P(N) = \\binom{n}{N}p^N(1-p)^{n-N},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:40 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`n` is the number of trials, :math:`p` is the probability of "
"success, and :math:`N` is the number of successes."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`n` 是试验次数，:math:`p` 是成功的概率，:math:`N` 是成功的次数"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.binomial.binomial:43 of
msgid ""
"When estimating the standard error of a proportion in a population by "
"using a random sample, the normal distribution works well unless the "
"product p*n <=5, where p = population proportion estimate, and n = number"
" of samples, in which case the binomial distribution is used instead. For"
" example, a sample of 15 people shows 4 who are left handed, and 11 who "
"are right handed. Then p = 4/15 = 27%. 0.27*15 = 4, so the binomial "
"distribution should be used in this case."
msgstr ""
"在使用随机样本估计总体比例的标准误差时，正态分布效果良好，除非乘积 p*n <="
"5，其中 p = 总体比例估计值，n = 样本数量，此时使用二项分布代替。例如，15 "
"人的样本中显示 4 人是左撇子，11 人是右撇子。则 p = 4/15 = 27%。0.27*15 = "
"4，因此在这种情况下应使用二项分布。"

